item.description: Alisa has asked that I post this event and she will be the group contact person for questions. Alisa's phone number is 760-550-0575. Join Alisa at the Village Cafe http://villagecafenh.... this Sunday, Oct 25, at 1PM for a Sunday brunch that will include Jazz Music, non-alchoholic drinks, appetizers, entree, breads and deserts. Total cost for everything is $20. This sounds like a nice way to spend a Sunday afternoon. I wish I could attend but have to be at work. Enjoy.
